## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest developments in drug policy and treatment. The complexity of drug abuse requires ongoing research and adaptation of strategies to effectively address the issue. Additionally, cultural and regional differences may influence the applicability of certain solutions.